<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_372_r1l2">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / VVir ſchicken cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l3">vnſer lıeb <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſellen / wılhelm Mendell / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l4">Stephan Coler / mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden cʒu reden von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l5">vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kaufflewte notdurfft / als ſie <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l6"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wol ercʒelen ſüllen / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / vvaʒ <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_372_r1l7"><expan>Ratgeſelle<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒu dıſem mal an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>durch<ex>leuhtikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
