<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir schicken czu
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden unser lieb
                                <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und ratgesellen Wilhelm Mendell und
                        Stephan Coler, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden czu reden von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
                        kaufflewte notdurfft, als sie <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wol erczelen süllen. Und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, waz
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ratgeselle<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czu disem mal an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>durch<ex>leuhtikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>werb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen, daz
                        sie <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade darynne
                            <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> und in des <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und sie auch darümb <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vertigen wöllet. Als etc. Das wöllen
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Elisabet<ex>hae</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>;<lb/> herczog
                                <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
